name: 1 bedroom apartment in South End
neighborhood_overview: It’s close to Tremont Street and Massachusetts Avenue, the main streets to get around in the city.
description:
Cozy apartment in South End . The apartment is very clean and close to transportation, shopping, bikes for rent, park, Museum of Fine Art, Fenway, Boston Medical Center, Northeastern University, BU Medical.

The space
You have the whole apartment on the third floor of the building

Guest access
The whole apartment

Other things to note
It’s easy to get anywhere around Boston.
